title: League of Legends: The 2021 One For All Tier List
content: Since the last time One for All Mode came out, back in Patch 10.7, six champions have been added to League of Legends – Lillia, Yone, Samira, Seraphine, and Viego. That’s not even counting the next League of Legends champion, Gwen, who will be dropping next patch. With all these new champions to play around with in One for All, we need to update our One for All tier list for 2021!
